{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1504,"text":"When you walk around\nthe place where you live,"},{"time":3921,"text":"most of the times,"},{"time":5374,"text":"you feel pretty safe\nand comfortable, right?"},{"time":8839,"text":"Now imagine if there were land mines"},{"time":11936,"text":"buried right here,"},{"time":14133,"text":"scattered around,"},{"time":15785,"text":"and you'd never know\nwhen you might step on one."},{"time":20100,"text":"That's how it is for many\nin my home country, Colombia."},{"time":23393,"text":"As a result of a 50-year\ninternal armed conflict,"},{"time":27147,"text":"we have an undetermined\nnumber of land mines"},{"time":29608,"text":"buried throughout the countryside,"},{"time":31529,"text":"affecting more than one third\nof the Colombian population."},{"time":36186,"text":"These anti-personnel mines"},{"time":39454,"text":"are designed to maim,\nnot to kill their targets."},{"time":43769,"text":"The logic behind this, which is awful,"},{"time":47194,"text":"is that more resources are taken up\ncaring for an injured soldier"},{"time":51794,"text":"than dealing with a person\nwho has been killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55348,"text":"I met Adriana Rodriguez\nabout five years ago"},{"time":59815,"text":"while I was working\nfor the Colombian government"},{"time":62106,"text":"as a documentary filmmaker."},{"time":64374,"text":"During the conflict,"},{"time":66054,"text":"she was forced to leave her house ..."},{"time":69268,"text":"with her kids in her arms."},{"time":72118,"text":"One day, one of her neighbors was killed"},{"time":75484,"text":"while he stepped on a land mine."},{"time":80406,"text":"He was actually inside\nan abandoned house, not outside,"},{"time":84582,"text":"a house exactly like the one\nAdriana was forced to leave."},{"time":88442,"text":"Ever since, she has been living\nwith the fear that she, or her children,"},{"time":92885,"text":"might step on a land mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95855,"text":"You know, the Colombian conflict\nhas been running for so long"},{"time":99092,"text":"that neither me nor my mom\nhave seen our country in peace,"},{"time":104481,"text":"and for someone like me,"},{"time":105973,"text":"who has been living detached\nfrom all this suffering,"},{"time":109458,"text":"there was only two options:"},{"time":112778,"text":"either I get used to it,"},{"time":114835,"text":"or I can try to change it\nwith all my heart."},{"time":119989,"text":"And I have to admit\nthat for almost 30 years,"},{"time":122672,"text":"I was getting used to it, you know?"},{"time":126694,"text":"But something changed for me\nwhen I met my wife."},{"time":130614,"text":"She is a political scientist"},{"time":132473,"text":"completely passionate\nabout the Colombian armed conflict."},{"time":136083,"text":"She helped me to understand"},{"time":138068,"text":"how deeply our country has\nbeen affected by land mines and by war."},{"time":143166,"text":"We decided to come here\nto the United States"},{"time":145783,"text":"in search of new skills"},{"time":147855,"text":"that would enable us to contribute\nin a fair way to our society,"},{"time":152109,"text":"and maybe even help heal it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155364,"text":"While in grad school,"},{"time":156559,"text":"I started developing"},{"time":157793,"text":"an augmented reality,\nreally broad application"},{"time":160857,"text":"to help military personnel\nto deactivate land mines more safely."},{"time":165583,"text":"During that time, I also realized"},{"time":168235,"text":"that Colombia is not\nthe only country in the world"},{"time":170886,"text":"that has to worry about land mines."},{"time":174724,"text":"In fact, more than 58 countries"},{"time":177593,"text":"are still contaminated\nwith any sort of explosive device."},{"time":182101,"text":"Only in 2015, due to an escalation of war"},{"time":185697,"text":"in countries like Libya,\nSyria, Ukraine and Yemen,"},{"time":189752,"text":"the number of [land mine\ncasualties] almost doubled,"},{"time":192372,"text":"from 3,695 to 6,461 people."},{"time":199051,"text":"Imagine that."},{"time":200259,"text":"While some countries\nare trying to get rid of land mines,"},{"time":203219,"text":"some others are increasing their use."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206648,"text":"But what happens when a conflict\nthat involved land mines"},{"time":210768,"text":"comes to an end?"},{"time":212782,"text":"There are two consequences."},{"time":214989,"text":"On the one hand,"},{"time":216672,"text":"the internally displaced population\nwill start returning to their lands,"},{"time":221384,"text":"and on the other hand,"},{"time":223256,"text":"hidden land mines are going\nto start exploding more often"},{"time":226915,"text":"on the civilian side."},{"time":229033,"text":"That's the reason why I decided to join"},{"time":231827,"text":"the Computer Science Department at NYU,"},{"time":234438,"text":"along with Professor Claudio Silva"},{"time":237151,"text":"to start to develop an app\ncalled MineSafe."},{"time":240831,"text":"MineSafe uses information\nfrom the community"},{"time":246380,"text":"to suggest paths that have been declared\nas the most transited"},{"time":250895,"text":"without accident or incident\ncaused by a land mine."},{"time":255035,"text":"These traffic patterns\ncan also be used to determine"},{"time":258686,"text":"the top priority zones to be de-mined."},{"time":263666,"text":"Almost 15 million people are living now\nin the countryside of Colombia."},{"time":269085,"text":"Imagine, for a moment, if we can\ncrowdsource information from all of them"},{"time":273611,"text":"to help people like Adriana\nand her children"},{"time":276705,"text":"to find safe and reliable paths."},{"time":279222,"text":"This information\ncan not only be used for that."},{"time":282032,"text":"This information can also help them\nto become more productive."},{"time":286379,"text":"Farmers will be able to find"},{"time":288533,"text":"which lands have been cleared\nfrom explosive devices,"},{"time":292570,"text":"and in that way, they will be able\nto find new, fertile grounds"},{"time":297857,"text":"to start growing food again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301212,"text":"MineSafe has now a partnership\nwith the Colombian government"},{"time":304579,"text":"for the initial pilot,"},{"time":306396,"text":"and we have now some connections\nwith Cambodia and Somalia as well."},{"time":311485,"text":"This project is being funded\nby private money"},{"time":313913,"text":"here in the United States,"},{"time":315859,"text":"but we don't want to stop here."},{"time":317708,"text":"We want to go big,"},{"time":319256,"text":"and we want to scale the project\nto every single place"},{"time":322603,"text":"where land mines are still a threat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326709,"text":"The Colombian armed conflict\nis finally coming to an end,"},{"time":331255,"text":"but the consequences of years of war\nare still buried under our feet."},{"time":336887,"text":"We at MineSafe are working\nto help both people and land"},{"time":342191,"text":"to find peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343848,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345023,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}